Well I haven't talked to Christina in a long time, and I miss her I just hope that she will read this because I will be able to drive by october so if I have to I will drive to her to see her!I just have this funny feeling that we should see eachother, like we are meant to meet eachother, sometime. well enough of this philosophy stuff, well I will write again~! Luv Ya, 
   Kyle
P.S. Kristina if u read this e-mail me hun mine aren't goin' through!

Ok there was an accident I was involved in on June 29, 2001. and I was the driver without a licence, well aparently I was not going to be charged or sued or anythin' well!!! Just today not long ago I find out that we could be sued  up to $40,000, well fuck I am in the shit hole! I can't believe it, well it just might be the time to call a buddy of mine and make some serious cash! It may not be a good place to go, but it'll pay off my debt! Fuck Fuck Fuck, now we  are being sued!! Damn it!!

Kristina if you read this I luv ya, and I might talk to you a lot about it, but thats because I can look to you and I know you'll listen(: I just want you to be there for me:) I'd really love that, and you know I care for you a lot, I will get through this no matter what I have to do!! but eventually, I will see you, and I will hold you in my arms:) well if ya can e-mail me :) I'd love to hear from ya since I haven't been on-line for a while:) well I love ya, *Lotsa Kisses*
                                  Love,
                                       Kyle
P.S. Li amo, bella signora ---}---@

Holy damn I just woke up, and I was thinkin' about what happened last night.  Well my best friend Matt and his Bro Giu (Giuliano), are like brothers to me, that is why I had helped Matt'd g/f to stop herself from doin' crazy shit.  Plus my bro(matt) and I had a chat about how I should get closer with my parents , and then maybe they'll like me, ha! Ya right! Everything about me everything I do, it is what they despise the most, I can really ony seek love within' others, whether it is friend, or girlfriend. Yes that would be you Kristina, and of course my 2 bro's! They've always been there for me and I hope it can be the same between me and Kristina, just a little different, but we won't get into that! You know I luv ya Kristina! And as long as we keep in touch, etc. I will always be there for you Kristina, in everyway!
anyway  Laterz, Kyle ---}---@

P.S. I know you didn't forget about me Kristina!! lol, hehehe

I have created an account here cause there's this real cutie, and she's got an account, I get to read about her yet she doesn't get to read about me so I'm writin' it in here, then she can read about my life too!! Luv ya Kristina!!
